<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: auto;">
        <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="DevGo Logo" style="width: 150px; display: block; margin-bottom: 20px;" />
        
        <h3>Payment Required for Order #{{trackingNumber}}</h3>
        
        <p>Hello {{customerName}},</p>
        <p>Your manual order has been created. To confirm your booking, please complete the payment of <strong>Rs. {{totalCharges}}</strong> by clicking the secure link below.</p>
        
        <a href="{{paymentUrl}}" target="_blank" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 25px; background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">
            Pay Now
        </a>

        <p>This link is valid for 24 hours.</p>
        <p>Thank you,<br>The DevGo Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>